\v 2 Ngizakuthi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: \add Uy\add*isiphephelo sami\x + 91.9. Hlab. 94.22. Hlab. 14.6. Hlab. 9.9.\x* lenqaba yami\x + Hlab. 31.3. 71.3. 144.2. 2 Sam. 22.2.\x*, uNkulunkulu wami, engithemba kuye\x + Hlab. 25.2.\x*.
\v 3 Sibili yena uzakukhulula\x + Zaga 6.5. Seb. 12.11.\x* emjibileni womthiyi\x + Jobe 18.9. Hlab. 69.22. 119.110. 124.7. 140.5. 141.9. 142.3. Hos. 5.1. 9.8. Hlab. 11.6.\x*, kuye umatshayabhuqe wesifo obhubhisayo\x + Hlab. 52.2.\x*.
\v 4 Uzakusibekela ngensiba zakhe\x + Jobe 39.13.\x*, uzathembela langaphansi kwempiko zakhe\x + Ruthe 2.12. Mat. 23.37. Luka 13.34.\x*\x + Hlab. 17.8. Hlab. 121.5.\x*\x + Jobe 39.13.\x*; iqiniso lakhe liyisihlangu lehawu\x + Hlab. 35.2.\x*.
\v 5 Kawuyikwesaba isesabiso sebusuku, umtshoko ophaphayo emini\x + Jobe 5.19,23. Zaga 3.23-26. Isa. 43.2.\x*,
\v 6 umatshayabhuqe wesifo ohambayo emnyameni\x + Jobe 10.22.\x*, incithakalo ebhubhisayo emini enkulu\x + Dute. 32.24. Isa. 28.2. Hos. 13.14.\x*.
\v 7 Bazakuwa abayinkulungwane eceleni kwakho, labayizinkulungwane ezilitshumi ngakwesokunene sakho; kuwe kakuyikusondela.
