\v 8 Uzakhangela nje ngamehlo akho, ubone impindiselo kwababi\x + Hlab. 37.34. Mal. 1.5.\x*.
\v 9 Ngoba wena, N\nd kosi\nd*, uyisiphephelo sami\x + 91.9. Hlab. 94.22. Hlab. 14.6. Hlab. 9.9.\x*; umenzile oPhezukonke waba yindawo yakho yokuhlala\x + Dute. 33.27.\x*.
\v 10 Kakulabubi obuzakwehlela\x + Zaga 12.21. Jobe 5.19.\x*, lenhlupheko kayiyikusondela\x + Hlab. 38.11.\x* ethenteni lakho\x + Jobe 8.22.\x*.
\v 11 Ngoba uzalaya\x + Mat. 4.6. Luka 4.10,11.\x* ingilosi zakhe ngawe, ukuthi zikulondoloze endleleni zakho zonke\x + Hlab. 34.7. Mat. 18.10.\x*.
\v 12 Zizakuphatha ezandleni, hlezi utshayeke ngonyawo lwakho elitsheni\x + Zaga 3.23. Hlab. 37.24.\x*.
\v 13 Uzanyathela\x + Luka 10.19.\x* isilwane lebululu\x + Jobe 10.16.\x*, uzagxoba ibhongo lesilwane, lomgobho\x + Hlab. 74.13.\x*.
