\v 14 Ngoba uyangithanda kakhulu, ngakho ngizamkhulula\x + Hlab. 22.9.\x*; ngizambeka phezulu\x + Hlab. 20.1.\x*, ngoba uyalazi ibizo lami\x + Hlab. 9.10.\x*.
\v 15 Uzangibiza, njalo ngimphendule; ngibe laye ekuhluphekeni\x + Jobe 12.4. Hlab. 50.15. Hlab. 107.6.\x*, ngimkhulule\x + Hlab. 50.15.\x*, ngimnike udumo\x + Hlab. 50.15.\x*\x + 1 Sam. 2.30 Joha. 12.26.\x*.
\v 16 Ngizamsuthisa ngobude bezinsuku, ngimtshengise usindiso lwami\x + Dute. 6.2. 1 Kho. 3.14.\x*.
